data.description: If your looking for a home near the beach, look no more! 10 minutes from Naples Beaches and Downtown 5th Ave. A tiled floor 3 bedroom, 2 bath and 1 car garage home with pool. A metal roof that can last a very long time, this home is in a great location! Right next to Sugden Regional Park that has a 60-acre lake with a beach, paddle boat rentals, walking path around the lake and so much more. And near U.S Open Pickleball park. Walking distances to restaurants, shopping or the Pharmacy. If your a boater there is a boat ramp 5 minutes away called Bayview Park 5 minutes to the Gulf. Great sunsets and enjoy salt water fishing from the park. The neighborhood is right off 41, Tamiami Trail that leads straight into 5th Ave Old Naples Downtown.
